data.description: Welcome to the Historic Cathedral Area. 509 Campbell Street is a historic home in the Upper Bluff that boasts 1,488 square feet, 4 well sized bedrooms, 2 full updated bathrooms. Original wood floors throughout this charming home with oak trim and pillars. Updated kitchen with plenty of cabinet space with ceramic tile flooring, full unfinished basement, well sized fenced in yard with a newly built 2.5 car garage. Prime location with many amenities nearby. Come and get the keys to this beautiful home, to call yours! Location is key, nearby - schools, public transportation, highway access to I-80, restaurants, casino, stores and much more. The Cathedral Area neighborhood of Joliet, IL is a green, tree-lined community that contains an incredible array of homes displaying a dozen architectural styles and this one can be YOURS! Currently occupied, home will be vacant end of December.
